      "content": "Hey, I just went through the Q3 audit report for FraudWatch. The discrepancy levels are way too high. Your flags are disproportionately hitting specific ethnic neighborhoods and demographics, and the error rate for those groups is causing a massive backlog in the compliance department. We need to discuss why your logic is so heavily skewed.",
