    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The transition isn't about \"support,\" it's about accuracy. The blinded system is designed specifically to remove the very demographic variables you're using to flag people. We aren't looking for a pilot program; we're looking to move to a more ethical, unbiased standard. Why should we keep using your logic if it's fundamentally flawed along these lines?",
